Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00

; Disables SysMain (formerly Superfetch).
; Preloads frequently used apps into RAM to speed up launches.
; On SSD: useless, wastes RAM and causes background disk I/O.
; On HDD: can improve app launch times — consider keeping it enabled.

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\SysMain]
"Start"=dword:00000004
